title: Doctor Who - Big Finish Podcast 04 - 02-27-2008
description:
Doctor Who - Big Finish Podcast 04 - 02-27-2008

This week in the Big Finish Podcast we feature Sarah Jane Smith as both audio series are released on download. Later in the show, we have Big Finish author and Torchwood scriptwriter, Joe Lidster giving us his top 5 recommendations from the Big Finish catalogue. And finally, like every week, we have your feedback and give you the latest in what&#039;s happening here at Big Finish.

Featured this week:

Sarah Jane Smith
The Chimes of Midnight
Creatures of Beauty
Project: Twilight
The Harvest
Doctor Who and the Pirates
